_sText:
Map inspired by love of sa_treetops
4 Levels and spawn points in each tower(8T;8CT)
AWP on raised platform in central area accessible by water climb
Scout, can NOT penetrate outer walls of towers, but can the inner
Pipes and Ventilation ducts can be used as bridges from tower to tower
Comes with completed .nav file for bot de-retardification(As much as thats possible)
